---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service">

  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-20 md:py-28 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
   
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <div class="inline-block mb-4 px-4 py-2 bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900/30 text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">
            ðŸ“„ Legal Notice
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 dark:text-white leading-tight">
            Afrodoctor <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400">Terms of Use</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">Last Updated: October {currentYear}</p>
    </div>

    <p class="mb-8 text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed p-6 border-l-4 border-blue-400 dark:border-blue-500 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 rounded-xl shadow-inner">
      These Terms of Use ("Terms") govern your access to and use of the **Afrodoctor** mobile and web applications and the Hospital Management system, owned and operated by **Health Solutions Ventures (HSV)**. By using Afrodoctor, you agree to be bound by these Terms and our Privacy Policy.
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-12">
       
        <div class="group">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 flex items-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                <span class="mr-3 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 group-hover:text-red-600 dark:group-hover:text-red-400 transition-colors duration-300">1.</span>
                Acceptance of Terms
            </h2>
            <p class="mb-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                By creating an account, logging in, or otherwise using the Afrodoctor system, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to comply with these Terms of Use and the Privacy Policy of the application.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="group">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 flex items-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                <span class="mr-3 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 group-hover:text-red-600 dark:group-hover:text-red-400 transition-colors duration-300">2.</span>
                User Accounts and Security
            </h2>
            <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-4 p-6 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <li class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                    <strong class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">Account Creation:</strong> Clients must create an account using their email or telephone contacts and a **strong password**. Backend users will be granted access by HSV as stipulated in Memoranda of Understanding.
                </li>
                <li class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                    <strong class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">Login Requirement:</strong> Users must log in for each session to use the service.
                </li>
                <li class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                    <strong class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">Password Reset:</strong> Clients who forget their passwords must follow an **identity verification process** before they can reset them.
                </li>
                <li class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                    <strong class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">Accountability:</strong> All parties with authorized access are accountable for their actions. Usernames and passwords must be kept secret, and users should **avoid clicking suspicious links**.
                </li>
                <li class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                    <strong class="text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">Unauthorized Access:</strong> Any unauthorized access will be promptly investigated, and **corrective disciplinary and/or technical action** will be taken.
                </li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <div class="group">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 flex items-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                <span class="mr-3 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 group-hover:text-red-600 dark:group-hover:text-red-400 transition-colors duration-300">3.</span>
                Data Management and Privacy
            </h2>
            <p class="mb-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                HSV places the highest importance on protecting patient/client health information, ensuring confidentiality, privacy, and integrity. Security and privacy controls are **compliant with Uganda's Data Protection and Privacy Act 2019 and Data Protection and Privacy Regulations, 2020.**
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="group">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 flex items-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                <span class="mr-3 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 group-hover:text-red-600 dark:group-hover:text-red-400 transition-colors duration-300">4.</span>
                Use of Afrodoctor
            </h2>
            <p class="mb-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                Afrodoctor enables clients to find needed medical services, products, and personnel; **book appointments** at partner health facilities or make **online medical consultations**; and may purchase needed sexual and reproductive health products at a reasonable fee.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="group">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 flex items-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                <span class="mr-3 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 group-hover:text-red-600 dark:group-hover:text-red-400 transition-colors duration-300">5.</span>
                Application Development and Operation
            </h2>
            <p class="mb-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                HSV aims to build the Afrodoctor system to operate without producing errors, though this cannot be guaranteed. The system is **upgradeable** and aims for **transparency** in process and operation.
            </p>
        </div>
       
        <div class="group">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 flex items-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                <span class="mr-3 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 group-hover:text-red-600 dark:group-hover:text-red-400 transition-colors duration-300">6.</span>
                Community Engagement
            </h2>
            <p class="mb-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                Feedback from users will be considered for any necessary changes that need to be made by HSV.
            </p>
        </div>
       
        <div class="group">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 flex items-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                <span class="mr-3 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 group-hover:text-red-600 dark:group-hover:text-red-400 transition-colors duration-300">7.</span>
                Intellectual Property
            </h2>
            <p class="mb-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                All content, features, and functionality within Afrodoctor are the **exclusive property of HSV** or its content suppliers and are protected by applicable intellectual property laws. Users may not reproduce or redistribute content except as permitted through the application's functionality.
            </p>
        </div>
       
        <div class="group">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 flex items-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                <span class="mr-3 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 group-hover:text-red-600 dark:group-hover:text-red-400 transition-colors duration-300">8.</span>
                International Health Data Regulations
            </h2>
            <p class="mb-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                While Afrodoctor primarily operates under Uganda's Data Protection laws, HSV strives to adhere to **international best practices** such as GDPR and HIPAA where applicable.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="group">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 flex items-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                <span class="mr-3 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 group-hover:text-red-600 dark:group-hover:text-red-400 transition-colors duration-300">9.</span>
                Indemnity
            </h2>
            <p class="mb-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                Users agree to defend, indemnify, and hold harmless HSV and its affiliates from any claims arising from violations of these Terms or **unauthorized access due to user negligence.**
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="group">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 flex items-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                <span class="mr-3 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 group-hover:text-red-600 dark:group-hover:text-red-400 transition-colors duration-300">10.</span>
                Compliance and Regulatory Requirements
            </h2>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed p-6 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 rounded-xl border border-blue-200 dark:border-blue-800">
                <li class="ml-2">Computer Misuse Act 2011</li>
                <li class="ml-2">Electronic Signature Act 2011</li>
                <li class="ml-2">Electronic Transactions Act 2011</li>
                <li class="ml-2"><strong class="text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300">Data Protection and Privacy Act 2019</strong></li>
                <li class="ml-2">National Information Technology policy 2009</li>
                <li class="ml-2">Data Protection and Privacy Regulations 2021</li>
                <li class="ml-2">Electronics Transaction Regulations 2013</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
       
        <div class="group">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 flex items-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                <span class="mr-3 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 group-hover:text-red-600 dark:group-hover:text-red-400 transition-colors duration-300">11.</span>
                Conclusion
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                This document outlines the guidelines to ensure safe, high-quality, and effective healthcare services through Afrodoctor. Violation of these guidelines carries associated risks for the user.
            </p>
        </div>

    </div>

  </section>

</BaseLayout>